<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.275965>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1. A – L: Rhabdotalebra litoralensis sp. nov. A, forewing; B, hindwing. Male: C – H. C, sternal apodeme; D, pygofer, lateral view; E, subgenital plate; F, connective; G, style; H, aedeagus, lateral view. Female: I – L. I, sternite VII; J, pygofer; K, large valve; L, small valve. (Figs A – C: 10 X; D – J: 20 X; K – L: 40 X) Scale bar = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275965/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

